Class ResourcesProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g04.model.ResourcesProvider

  • public class ResourcesProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that provides resources instead of hardcoding them each time we need one and to avoid a lot of SQL queries and disk access.
